Package: amap
Type: Package
Title: An R package using AMap API
Version: 0.1.5
Author: Xiaojun Lin <linxiaojun@scu.edu.cn>
Maintainer: Xiaojun Lin <linxiaojun@scu.edu.cn>
Description: This R package provides useful map tools for social science research using the AMap API. You can use it to getting the coordinates for the given addresses, converting the coordinates to the addresses, and calculating the travel distance between different addresses. 
URL: https://github.com/xiaojunlin/amap
